article: IBM BPM相关红宝书


	IBM发布有很多BPM相关的红宝书，可以作为参考，例如：

	1. {Business Process Management Design Guide: Using IBM Business Process Manager}(https://www.redbooks.ibm.com/abstracts/sg248282.html)
	2. {Scaling BPM Adoption: From Project to Program with IBM Business Process Manager}(https://www.redbooks.ibm.com/abstracts/SG247973.html)
	3. {Applying Lean, Six Sigma, BPM, and SOA to Drive Business Results}(https://www.redbooks.ibm.com/abstracts/redp4447.html)
	4. {Creating a BPM Center of Excellence (CoE)}(https://www.redbooks.ibm.com/abstracts/redp4898.html)

	还有一些和IBM的BPM产品相关性较强的文档：

	1. {Business Process Management Deployment Guide Using IBM Business Process Manager V8.5}(https://www.redbooks.ibm.com/abstracts/sg248175.html)
	2. {IBM Business Process Manager Version 8.0 Production Topologies}(https://www.redbooks.ibm.com/abstracts/sg248135.html)
	2. {IBM Business Process Manager V8.5 Performance Tuning and Best Practices}(https://www.redbooks.ibm.com/abstracts/sg248216.html)
	3. {Deliver Modern UI for IBM BPM with the Coach Framework and Other Approaches}(https://www.redbooks.ibm.com/Redbooks.nsf/RedpieceAbstracts/sg248355.html)

	更多文档，可以查看{这里}(https://www.redbooks.ibm.com/Redbooks.nsf/domains/smarterprocess)。

	另外，Oracle的{文档}(https://docs.oracle.com/middleware/1213/bpm/)也可以参考。
